==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Frangulin
<hw>Fran"gu*lin</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>A yellow crystalline dyestuff, regarded as a glucoside, extracted
from a species (<spn>Rhamnus Frangula</spn>) of the buckthorn; -- called
also <altname>rhamnoxanthin</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Franion</ent>⟦br⟧
